<p>Hmmm... I guess that would require some kind of wrapper script. As far as I know, scp doesn't feature exclude support. The program <a href="http://rsync.samba.org/">rsync</a> does, though, so maybe it is worth the time to look into it.</p>
<p>I don't know what you mean with "how to scp a symbolic link without copying all the links?", but maybe the -p option (preserve) might help.</p>
