				  <div class="text"><p>You can specify the username using the username@hostname syntax, and using scp without entering a password is very well possible. Just get ssh to work without a password and scp should do so, too. Search the net for "passwordless ssh" to find howto's on it. Be careful, though; passwordless ssh has some security concerns.</p>
