				 <span><strong><a href='http://ducquoc.wordpress.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>DucQuoc.wordpress.com</a></strong> </span>November 8, 2010 at 12:46 				
				  <div class="text"><p>thanks ! all are useful commands :-) </p>
<p>Is there some simple method to copy file through some kind of "ssh chain" ?<br />
Assuming that I'm at "homepc" , can connect via SSH to "remote1" , and from "remote1" I can connect SSH to "remote2" .<br />
Which is the "one-liner" to copy a file from "remote2" to "homepc" ?<br />
