 </div>
				   			<div class="reply">
					 <a class='comment-reply-link' href='http://www.linuxtutorialblog.com/post/ssh-and-scp-howto-tips-tricks?replytocom=4287#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-4287", "4287", "respond", "1")'>Reply</a>				  </div>
